We've heard of games doing this before, but you have to stop rendering mid-frame for a while to do a second sprite DMA. Very few PPU operations can be performed while rendering is on and not cause glitches.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Mon Jul 09, 2007 4:32 pm</p><hr />
